            "value": "<p>We represent a new way of doing things.</p><p>The opaque, complex process behind offshoring and international trade has always been the perfect condition for swindlers and imposters to thrive. Each year, hundreds of businesses spend millions of dollars to maintain reliable offshoring teams and/or agents, who seem to know what they are paid to do, yet still reluctant to reveal their most valuable secrets.</p><p> It’s time for Leshy Vision to raise the bar and push for more transparency.</p>",
